window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>They were the Three Amigos: Duncan Holloway, Imogen Swan, and Corey Szabo. Two young boys with difficult lives at home banding together with a cool girl who didn’t mind mucking through the mud on their hikes. </p> <p>They grew up to be Duncan Holloway, activist, CEO, and face of the popular River Rain outdoor stores, Imogen Swan, award-winning actress and America’s sweetheart, and Corey Szabo, ruthless tech billionaire. </p> <p>Rich and very famous, they would learn the devastating knowledge of how the selfish acts of one would affect all their lives. </p> <p>And the lives of those they loved. </p> <p>Start the River Rain series with <i>After the Climb</i>, the story of Duncan and Imogen navigating their way back to each other, decades after a fierce betrayal. </p> <p>And introduce yourself to their families, who will have their stories told when River Rain continues.</p>"; 
